OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine warm
OL,6,Fsunny evening in all areas then a dry
OL,7,Fnight with some long clear spells.
OL,8,FSome patchy mist around dawn and
OL,9,Fperhaps clouding over towards Mull.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FAnother dry day. There will
OL,12,Fbe some good spells of sunshine, but a
OL,13,Fcloudier period is possible around the
OL,14,Fmiddle of the day.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FIt will
OL,17,Fbe a dry few days with variable cloud
OL,18,Fand some sunny spells. Mainly light
OL,19,Fwinds, and on the warm side.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
